These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade
The people have 2 different hobbies: reading, photography
The people have 2 different jobs:  librarian, firefighter
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: musical, action
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, dutch
2 different pets are kept: snake, guinea-pig
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, van
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
2. the firefighter is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the van is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
4. the owner of the snake is the dutch##1
5. the person watching action movies is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |
| Beverage      | lemonade     | hot-chocolate       |
| Hobby         | reading   | photography     |
| Job           | librarian | firefighter   |
| Movie-Genre   | action   | musical  |
| Nationality   | dutch | canadian |
| Pet           | snake      | guinea-pig     |
| Transport     | van    | roller   |

