.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, 7up
The people have 2 different hobbies: baking, rock-climbing
The people have 2 different jobs:  videographer, engineer
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: house, electronic
There are 2 different nationalities: japanese, mexican
2 different pets are kept: cat, frog
The people use 2 different means of transport: subway, trike
1. the engineer is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the owner of the frog is the person driving the trike##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the left of the fan of house##1
4. the mexican is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking mirinda is the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | 7up |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing        | baking  |
| Job           | videographer | engineer  |
| Music-Genre   | electronic            | house    |
| Nationality   | japanese     | mexican   |
| Pet           | cat         | frog    |
| Transport     | subway           | trike      |

